OL,5, A former teacher accused by BBC        
OL,6, presenter Nicky Campbell and others of 
OL,7, abuse at schools in Edinburgh has      
OL,8, appeared in court in South Africa.     
OL,10,FThe 83-year-old, who cannot be named   
OL,11,Ffor legal reasons, was charged with    
OL,12,Findecent assault and committing an     
OL,13,Findecent act with a minor at a boys    
OL,14,Fprimary school in Cape Town in 1988.   
OL,16,FThe man, known in a BBC documentary as 
OL,17,F"Edgar", has denied claims against him.
OL,19,FHe was released pending a further      
OL,20,Fhearing.                               
